### Add New Skill

1. Create skill definition in `agents/skills/[role]/`
2. Update role's skills graph
3. Implement in `scripts/` (if rule-based) or `agents/skills/prompts/` (if LLM-based)
4. Test the skill

### Add New Behavior

1. Create behavior file in `.cursor/behaviors/[role]/`
2. Update `.cursor/rules.md` index
3. Update role's behaviors graph
4. Test with relevant workflow

